{"tid":1565724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解未有人咁樣鬧狗","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T14:19:27.000Z","uid":203743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b51158780caba0e76edda1b324cc41f616708b23","tid":1565724,"uid":203743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"「支(zhī)那(n&agrave;)豬(zhū)」<br />\n<br />\n有支那狗落嚟香港亂打市民、強姦義士，已經係公開嘅秘密。<br />\n<br />\n與其繼續屌嗰班本地狗紙老虎，倒不如直中要害，屌到班支那外判情緒唔穩定，越嚟越難被高層駕馭。佢哋癲狂再昇華，遲早出大新聞。<br />\n<br />\n再者，話唔定可以激到佢哋落單鳩衝出嚟打人，創造義士反打支那狗嘅機會。"},{"pid":"d8c68749d9088faa243c7b85ef77258eb963ef34","tid":1565724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ca50850a219f08b2c1e62afaeaa7fac3182f3ae1","tid":1565724,"uid":203743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"而家越嚟越多人相信狗隊混入咗好多支那狗<br />\n<br />\n大家捨得鬧支那狗未？佢哋暴打姦殺我哋香港市民，但你哋連兜口兜面鬧佢哋都未做到，一味剩係怪香港狗隊，有無諗過支那武狗而家係度恥笑我哋！"}]}